{"tid":285212,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"憎熱狗還憎熱狗, 但鄭松泰博士份學養真係唔講得笑","createTime":"2017-06-15T15:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T09:56:14.000Z","uid":76115,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6b802614b5dc965d2c97a85d24d06af23a8d0e3","tid":285212,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:05:05.000Z","msg":"由一二年熱狗崛起開始, 喺高登就日撚日見人吹奏鄭博士幾巴屎閉, 同阿緊開個節目講幾撚多名著理論睇幾撚多書, 本身重有啲懷疑<br />\n<br />\n一睇呢份公開信先知係真, 屌你老味讀博士讀到咁撚才華橫溢, 真係唔怪得有自信話香港大眾係白痴可以任得佢呢個政治家撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/16826062_718372338337126_1256468034664815028_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F16826062_718372338337126_1256468034664815028_o.jpg&h=b5f5d7a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/16903517_718372335003793_7380933932198908393_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F16903517_718372335003793_7380933932198908393_o.jpg&h=f7ad5ab5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bd803a8aeb2468491abd0e3ada5659c55d50588","tid":285212,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:26:57.000Z","msg":"北大"},{"pid":"4e4524722bf9115beb0312addd346001c831972d","tid":285212,"uid":10171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"大佬啲grammar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6678147dc76cce8e2d4b2b7d9ad80310836c7237","tid":285212,"uid":40463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"最尾個defense係咪錯grammar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" cla