=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCan Defense Be a Verb?<br />\n<br />\nIn any bit of formal writing, defense is not to be used as a verb.<br />\n<br />\nIt is, occasionally, used in sports related contexts to mean, &ldquo;defend against.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nThe Chicago Bulls defensed (defended against) the Detroit Pistons offense spectacularly tonight.<br />\nEven in sports related contexts it is uncommon and should be avoided. For example, The AP Stylebook says never to use defense as a verb.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://writingexplained.org/defence-vs-defense-difference\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwritingexplained.org%2Fdefence-vs-defense-difference&d=T%2FS5IpksPVt9v4yNcky7FviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=bdae88a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://writingexplained.org/defence-vs-defense-difference</a>"},{"pid":"3617b84fd90a8e220c51096df57f1b2dab0c73e1","tid":285212,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大佬啲grammar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最精彩係古德明有期專欄笑柒佢, 佢厚面皮到出返個status, 話篇野係趕時間快手寫成, 串柒古德明拎住本象牙塔爛字典捉佢字 etc.<br />\n明明篇文錯哂啲中學生基本野, 佢重講得出人地係象牙塔吹毛求疵, 呢啲撚樣畀成班智障熱狗圍住拜拜到以為自己真係好有料唔錯得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/columnist/2459936/art/20170311/19954152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F2459936%2Fart%2F20170311%2F19954152&d=T%2FS5IpksPVt9v4yNcky7FviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=4d5247a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fcolumnist%2F2459936%2Fart%2F20170311%2F1995